    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📥 Incoming Email Trigger\nThis section watches your Gmail inbox for **new incoming emails**.\n\n### What it does:\n- Checks Gmail every minute\n- Pulls sender, subject, snippet, and metadata\n- Starts the full automation\n\n### Why it matters:\nThis is the **entry point** of the workflow. Every new email begins here.",
        "height": 452,
        "width": 364,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "a206cc12-73b8-4f50-812e-0d717d2ac1eb",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Incoming",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1712,
        992
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🧹 Prepare Email Data\nThis section cleans and formats the email before sending it to AI.\n\n### It extracts:\n- Subject line\n- Sender name\n- Sender email\n- Snippet/body preview\n\n### Why it matters:\nAI performs much better when the email is passed in a **structured format** instead of raw Gmail output.",
        "height": 456,
        "width": 416,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "a7c1bc9e-b64a-46be-b00c-bd915058c2fc",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Prepare",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1248,
        992
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🧠 AI Email Classification Engine\nThis is the **main decision-making layer**.\n\n### It classifies emails into:\n- Promotional\n- Support\n- Order_Query\n- Job_Opportunity\n- Assignment\n- Spam\n\n### Output format:\nIt returns clean JSON with:\n- category\n- priority\n- reason\n\n### Why it matters:\nThis prevents you from manually sorting your inbox.",
        "height": 644,
        "width": 588,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "5a164761-5112-41a0-bce6-d2fe58abbafe",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Classifier",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -800,
        992
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🛡️ Output Parsing Safety Layer\nThis section ensures the AI output is **safe and usable**.\n\n### What it does:\n- Parses AI JSON response\n- Prevents workflow crashes\n- Falls back to `Spam` if output is invalid\n\n### Why it matters:\nWithout this, bad model output can break the workflow.",
        "height": 612,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "02c6e8e7-3573-4678-b2bd-06f4c27a731c",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Parser",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -192,
        992
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔀 Smart Routing by Category\nThis section decides **what should happen next** based on the email category.\n\n### Routing logic:\n- Support → AI Support Agent\n- Order_Query → AI Support Agent\n- Job_Opportunity → Telegram Alert\n- Assignment → Telegram Alert\n- Promotional → Optional Alert / Ignore\n- Spam → Ignore\n\n### Why it matters:\nThis makes the workflow fully automated and action-based.",
        "height": 660,
        "width": 460,
        "color": 7
      },
      "id": "ef8a5d90-45cf-4f94-bc95-e4979e1026e5",
      "name": "Sticky Note - Routing",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        208,
        992
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🤖 AI Support & Order Reply Assistant\nThis section handles emails that need a **proper response**.\n\n### It is used for:\n- Support emails\n- Order-related customer queries\n\n### What it does:\n- Understands the email\n- Uses your knowledge base\n- Drafts a professional reply\n\n### Why it matters:\nThis saves time and creates accurate customer support drafts.",
        "height": 596,
        "width": 508,
        "color": 4
      },
