    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📚 Vector Knowledge Base (RAG)\nThis section lets the AI search your stored support documents.\n\n### It can retrieve:\n- FAQs\n- Policies\n- Shipping info\n- Refund rules\n- Product info\n- Internal support knowledge\n\n### Why it matters:\nThis reduces hallucination and improves reply accuracy.",
        "height": 700,
